In this level, the password is stored in a hidden file inside a directory.

After logging in as bandit3, the home directory contained a folder named inhere.

To move into that directory, the following
->command was used:cd inhere
To list all files including hidden files, 
->the command used was:ls -a
A hidden file named .hidden was found.
To read the contents of the hidden file, the following
->command was used:cat .hidden
The file contained the password for the next level.
->Flag / Password for Level 4:2WmrDFRmJIq3IPxneAaMGhap0pFhF3NJ
